# üîê Environment Variables for Netlify Deployment
# Copy these to your Netlify Dashboard ‚Üí Site Settings ‚Üí Environment Variables

# ===== REQUIRED FOR AI GOLF TUTOR =====
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-proj-your-openai-api-key-here

# ===== OPTIONAL FEATURES =====
# ElevenLabs for voice coaching (optional)
ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=your-elevenlabs-api-key-here

# Supabase for data storage (optional - leave blank if not using)
# IMPORTANT: Only set these if you have a real Supabase project!
# If you don't want to use Supabase, leave these commented out:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-real-anon-key-here
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-real-service-role-key-here

# ===== SITE CONFIGURATION =====
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://your-site-name.netlify.app
NODE_ENV=production
NEXT_TELEMETRY_DISABLED=1

# ===== ANALYTICS (OPTIONAL) =====
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX
NEXT_PUBLIC_GTM_ID=GTM-XXXXXXX

# ===== NETLIFY DEPLOYMENT NOTES =====

# üö® IMPORTANT: Supabase Configuration
# The app will work WITHOUT Supabase - it will use local fallback data
# Only configure Supabase if you want persistent data storage
# If you set placeholder values, the build will fail!

# ‚úÖ Quick Start (AI Golf Tutor only):
# 1. Set OPENAI_API_KEY with real key
# 2. Set NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL to your Netlify domain
# 3. Leave Supabase variables commented out
# 4. Deploy and test!

# ===== HOW TO GET API KEYS =====

# 1. OpenAI API Key (REQUIRED):
#    - Go to https://platform.openai.com
#    - Create account ‚Üí API Keys ‚Üí Create new secret key
#    - Copy the key starting with "sk-proj-"

# 2. ElevenLabs API Key (Optional for voice):
#    - Go to https://elevenlabs.io
#    - Sign up ‚Üí Profile ‚Üí API Key
#    - Copy your API key

# 3. Supabase Keys (Optional for database):
